node.text:
Is your dream suit so unique that only really you could design it? If so, we have a surprise for you! Introducing our D.I.Y. Swimsuit Kit. It comes with everything you need to sew your perfect suit from scratch. Sound crazy? It's easier than you'd think! Link in bio to find out more! 

#jolyn #diy #swimsuit

node.text:
@makaniadric is active in many action sports from boxing to jiu-jitsu and now riding massive big waves on the North Shore of Oahu! 🌊⁠
⁠
Makani was awarded runner-up at Yeti’s “People’s Choice Awards” as well as the Red-bull’s "Magnitude Award" for the Women’s Big Wave Contest. She inspires us to challenge ourselves physically and mentally because anything is possible once you put your heart and mind to it! ⁠
⁠
Makani is definitely a Woman Who Inspires us and is a reminder that we can all conquer big things! #jolyn Makani was nominated by our @jolynhawaii Rep! ⁠🌈⁠ @makaniadric
